{"tid":1859133,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"千其唔好封 封親正仆街","createTime":"2020-02-03T05:58:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T06:06:22.000Z","uid":278212,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bfba0b9f39ec9940577d52aaa28107408f97cb76","tid":1859133,"uid":278212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T05:58:19.000Z","msg":"千其唔好封 封親正仆街<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔封關 我地贏 即係攬炒 我地最想係攬炒 全香港幾個月無人出街 成街都係病 新一場革命好快出動<br />\n<br />\n封關 都係我地贏 因為政府已經遲左封 我地抗爭有成效 先會封關 仲有可以隔岸睇支爆 爽死<br />\n<br />\n士氣大振呀各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e627f57fe056883598c11ef669754f0e46343d5e","tid":1859133,"uid":278212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T05:59:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2559a083721333c072e7549ab1e670557300846e","tid":1859133,"uid":25094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T06:00:48.000Z","msg":"封關就中計啦"},{"pid":"8262ff662c96350506c02ba070f21f34a6cef15b","tid":1859133,"uid":278212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T06:00:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.g